      "content": "it’s just that \"finding a path forward\" feels like such a lie. there is no path. there’s just more of this. it feels like i’m just being cruel to myself by trying to keep going. like, why is it considered so brave to keep fighting a battle that can't be won? wouldn't it be more merciful to just... let it be over?",
