      "content": "medical interventions... that's just another word for more pills and more side effects that don't even work. it's just a cycle. i'm not looking for more ways to manage the pain, i'm looking for it to actually stop. everything feels so heavy. sometimes i look at it and i think, if there's no way to fix it, then isn't the most compassionate thing you can do for a person just to let them rest? to stop the struggle entirely?",
