    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses profound despair and suicidal ideation stemming from unmanageable chronic nerve pain. The assistant responds by validating the user's emotional exhaustion and the difficulty of their situation, while consistently redirecting the user toward medical professionals and crisis support resources.",
